				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/B%E1%BB%87nh-trung-du-T%E1%BB%95-Th%C3%A1p-vi%E1%BB%87n/poem-g7BAWHeMRD41JhBwDOtGZg">Bệnh trung du Tổ Tháp viện - 病中遊祖塔院</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/C%C3%A1t-lu%E1%BB%B9-3/poem-qh4BYBPBXYTP8jQuBfBCAg">Cát luỹ 3 - 葛藟 3</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/C%C6%B0u-m%E1%BB%99c-3/poem-xgUtI0x3DjkSILcMJqibiw">Cưu mộc 3 - 樛木 3</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/U%C3%B4ng-Uy%E1%BB%83n/%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Th%E1%BA%ADp-Nh%E1%BA%A5t-ph%C3%BA-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-giang-vi%C3%AAn-ng%C3%A2m-Thu%C3%BD-B%C3%ACnh-t%E1%BB%91ng-L%E1%BB%A5c-Ba-Ch%C3%A2u-chi-nh%E1%BA%ADm/poem-VcPHz7OpmGnrtOudXDG-YQ">Đồng Vương Thập Nhất phú đắc giang viên ngâm Thuý Bình tống Lục Ba Châu chi nhậm - 同王十一賦得江猿吟翠屏送陸巴州之任</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/U%C3%B4ng-Uy%E1%BB%83n/author-ibHJS1_sKCWaPA3O5x82_A">Uông Uyển</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Kho%C3%A1-ti%E1%BB%83u-th%E1%BB%A5-s%E1%BB%AB-ch%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bc-x%C3%A1-b%E1%BA%AFc-qu%E1%BA%A3-l%C3%A2m-chi-m%E1%BA%A1n-hoang-u%E1%BA%BF-t%E1%BB%8Bnh-ng%E1%BA%ADt-di-s%C3%A0ng-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-XM2SgmEcFWGaefrB5iIc-g">Khoá tiểu thụ sừ chước xá bắc quả lâm, chi mạn hoang uế, tịnh ngật di sàng kỳ 2 - 課小豎鋤斫舍北果林，枝蔓荒穢，淨訖移床三首其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Mao-kh%C3%A2u-1/poem-Ta1gOWTw5T5AdfrBQo4I1w">Mao khâu 1 - 旄丘 1</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-khanh-%C3%B4ng-th%E1%BB%89nh-tu-V%C5%A9-H%E1%BA%A7u-mi%E1%BA%BFu-di-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-khuy%E1%BA%BFt-l%E1%BA%A1c-th%C3%AC-Th%C3%B4i-khanh-quy%E1%BB%81n-Qu%E1%BB%B3-Ch%C3%A2u/poem-8fXKKYvUpOeQ5W_T-vthXA">Thượng khanh ông thỉnh tu Vũ Hầu miếu, di tượng khuyết lạc, thì Thôi khanh quyền Quỳ Châu - 上卿翁請修武侯廟，遺像缺落，時崔卿權夔州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Tu%C3%BD-h%E1%BA%ADu-cu%E1%BB%93ng-ng%C3%B4n-th%C3%B9-t%E1%BA%B7ng-Ti%C3%AAu-%C3%82n-nh%E1%BB%8B-hi%E1%BB%87p-lu%E1%BA%ADt/poem-9ZhJAi3DjT-FEtHvvFbdPw">Tuý hậu cuồng ngôn, thù tặng Tiêu, Ân nhị hiệp luật - 醉後狂言，酬贈蕭、殷二協律</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-ho%C3%A0i-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-3mvgQ8jqLVNdE0oNQACUCg">Vịnh hoài kỳ 2 - 詠懷其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Cung-Do%C3%A3n/X%C3%ADch-B%C3%ADch-chu-trung-ca/poem-js6oe3kPuWEg0IcUcHLCeg">Xích Bích chu trung ca - 赤壁舟中歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Cung-Do%C3%A3n/author-8wX_f--qBGvseLM4iD_Z7A">Trần Cung Doãn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
